    "name": "Shards of the Realm",
    "steam_appid": 3214790,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创造你自己的故事——管理你的队伍和要塞，探索、制作、缔结联盟，或者成为他们畏惧的敌人。<br><br><strong>Shards of the Realm</strong> 是一款复杂的老派 <u><strong>策略/战术角色扮演游戏</strong></u>，灵感来自经典的 X-Com 系列。游戏设有一个活生生的开放世界，战术与战略层面高度交织，提供超过 <strong>50 小时</strong> 的游戏内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建设你的堡垒，管理工人、交易、建造——一切都需要精明的战略规划。在战场上，灵活的职业系统、多职业、技能协同以及可破坏环境，带来了多样的战术选择。深入的研究与制作系统可让你为应对世界中的各种挑战做好准备。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战术战斗——物理、位置、破坏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/665227107e086e524829832a2f2a5208.poster.avif?t=1754714516\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/665227107e086e524829832a2f2a5208.webm?t=1754714516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/665227107e086e524829832a2f2a5208.mp4?t=1754714516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>无掷骰子，无抽象处理——真实弹道和物理碰撞驱动战斗。位置、掩体和单位间互动至关重要。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无格子</strong>、无固定行动数——行动点是你唯一的限制。任意分配。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一切都可以作为掩体</strong>：地形、树木，甚至盟友或敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>方向性护甲区域</strong>（正面、侧翼、背部）奖励聪明的包抄和伏击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>环境可破坏</strong>——炸毁掩体或开辟新道路。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>友军伤害</strong>开启——即使近战攻击也可能误伤盟友。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>构建你的小队——没有模板，只有你的战术</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/1eb34920899027afd4b25144923e7a46.poster.avif?t=1754714516\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/1eb34920899027afd4b25144923e7a46.webm?t=1754714516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/1eb34920899027afd4b25144923e7a46.mp4?t=1754714516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可控制 <strong>最多9名角色</strong> 的小队</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 个基础职业 + 8 个独特子职业，拥有 <strong>独特玩法</strong>、定位和技能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>支持多职业</strong>，拥有超过 60 个主动与被动技能的技能树</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入的状态效果系统：光环、增益、减益、协同</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有“正确”构筑——按你的方式打造英雄：传统坦克/输出/辅助，或是混合定位</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战略深度——你的要塞，你的规则</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/907c37f00e73af276d22df70b24d9900.poster.avif?t=1754714516\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/907c37f00e73af276d22df70b24d9900.webm?t=1754714516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/907c37f00e73af276d22df70b24d9900.mp4?t=1754714516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有掉落狂潮——几乎所有装备都通过研究与制作手工打造。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的堡垒</strong> 是经济、科研、招募与制作的核心</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 <strong>200 件各类物品</strong>：武器、盔甲、工具、戒指、交易品等可研发与生产</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>人力是你的主要资源</strong>——谁进实验室，谁进锻造厂，谁上战场？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 个NPC派系，拥有各自目标与冲突。你的选择将塑造政治版图——贸易、结盟或灭绝他们</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>昼夜循环</strong> 影响全球与战术层面的可见度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏的 <strong>地牢</strong>，拥有独特奖励与挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恶魔攻城</strong>——全球威胁也是战术机会。它们可以毁灭你的据点，也可以帮你铲除对手</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/1dd7fe0669143bbc80ee91b5c1cfb669.poster.avif?t=1754714516\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/1dd7fe0669143bbc80ee91b5c1cfb669.webm?t=1754714516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214790/extras/1dd7fe0669143bbc80ee91b5c1cfb669.mp4?t=1754714516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shards of the Realm</strong> 是一款每个错误都可能带来毁灭的游戏。<br>但如果你喜欢有意义的决策、深度机制与反应型世界——这就是为你而做的游戏。</p>",
